Slide 15 – Limitations of Docker Compose
Speaker Notes
“Although Docker Compose is very useful, it also has some limitations.
•	It works mainly on a single host machine
•	Not designed for large-scale production systems
•	Limited built-in monitoring and scaling features
For large production environments, tools like Kubernetes are often used.”



